## Timing Guide

| Segment | Duration | Activity |
|---------|----------|----------|
| Opening | 5 min | Welcome, agenda review, connect to prior learning |
| Theory Presentation | 30 min | Key concepts and statistical foundations |
| Software Demonstration | 15 min | Live walkthrough in Minitab/JMP/R |
| Guided Exercise | 20 min | Students work through exercise with instructor support |
| Independent Practice | 15 min | Students complete exercise independently |
| Review and Q&A | 5 min | Debrief, address questions, preview next module |
| **Total** | **90 min** |

